                                                                <comments>
                            <comment id="14617" author="juergen.hoeller" created="Thu, 8 Sep 2005 21:34:46 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Thanks for pointing this out! There is indeed the assumption that proper error codes are used. I&apos;ll make sure that this will work with null or invalid error codes as well.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Juergen&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14641" author="juergen.hoeller" created="Sat, 10 Sep 2005 06:13:59 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;BindStatus resolves error messages lazily now, to allow for custom error code resolution (avoid NoSuchMessageException). I&apos;ve added tests for both the code-only scenario and the default-only scenario, which all pass for me now. Please give one of the next nightly snapshots a try to check whether it works for you as well!&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Juergen&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
